column4: NSLOCTEXT("[36E9DC4C4BA8E7BFCFD52196932F5F80]", "B2BB424244B58C0BFEDAD8B6CB4EC4CE", "This costume seems different from others. It has some overpowering presence.")

NSLOCTEXT("[36E9DC4C4BA8E7BFCFD52196932F5F80]", "8E0047BD4138B3C030A1319183954293", "What? Did you turn into another Digimon? It\'s kinda nice.")
